description: Declarative form system
globs: src/app/core/form/**,src/**/*.form.ts,src/**/*form-page*
alwaysApply: false
---

# Forms (`src/app/core/form`)

1. Model: `*.model.ts` interface for form value.
2. Definition: `export const X = defineForm<Model>()({ mode: 'single'|'stepper', steps: [...] })`.
3. Page: `FormBuilder` group mirrors field keys; pass `[definition]` + `[form]` to `FormPageComponent`.
4. Options: `{ value, labelKey }`; field types: text, number, textarea, select, radio, checkbox, toggle.
5. Custom blocks: `formFieldKey` / `formSectionKey` / `formStepKey` + `*Template` directives in page HTML.
6. Submit: `form.getRawValue() as Model` (validators on `FormGroup`, not only in def).

Extend field types in `form-field-renderer` + `fields/form-*-field/`, not ad-hoc duplicate inputs on standard pages.
